多家媒体（《<a target="_blank" href="steam://openurl/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2013/11/valve-steam-machines/?cid=co13996514"><u>连线</u></a>》、<a target="_blank" href="steam://openurl/http://www.businessweek.com/news/2013-11-04/valve-lines-up-console-partners-in-challenge-to-microsoft-sony"><u>彭博社</u></a>、《<a target="_blank" href="steam://openurl/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/the-switch/wp/2013/11/04/valves-steam-machine-is-the-anti-console-heres-what-its-like-to-play/"><u>华盛顿邮报</u></a>》和<a target="_blank" href="steam://openurl/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/11/04/how-valve-engineered-the-perfect-controller"><u>IGN</u></a>等）访问了Valve总部，发布了SteamOS、Steam主机和手柄的<a target="_blank" href="http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2013/11/11-things-we-learned-from-valves-latest-steam-machine-pr-push/"><u>第一手试用报告</u></a>。Valve采用了一系列空气导流板确保主机内部组件不过热；SteamOS的使用体验与Steam客户端的Big Picture模式类似；Steam主机的更多信息将会在明年一月举行的CES大展上公布；手柄含有陀螺仪或能用于动作控制；《半条命3》不会是SteamOS独占——Valve的原话没有提到《半条命3》，只是表示SteamOS不会有独占的杀手级应用，Valve的杀手级游戏是《半条命3》；Valve的330名雇员中有40人参与Steam主机硬件的开发工作。
